      "name": "ASTM F1717 static compression-bending operating envelope",
      "description": "The validated operating envelope is bounded as follows: screw outer diameter 7.0–8.0 mm (nominal 7.5 mm ±0.25 mm machining tolerance); screw shank length 40–55 mm; connecting rod diameter 5.5 mm ±0.1 mm; polyaxial head angulation 0–15°; applied displacement rate 5 mm/min (quasi-static, strain-rate insensitive regime); peak applied force 0–2500 N; construct span 40 mm per ASTM F1717 §8.3; ambient temperature 20–25 °C; test medium dry air (no simulated body fluid). Models validated within this envelope only; extrapolation beyond any bound requires re-assessment."
    },
    "hasApplicabilityConstraint": {
